Text: Polifem, do you have "Abare Goemon/Rise against the sword" too? I am not sure if it has got a dvd release.
How about "Muhomatsu no issho" and "Machibuse"? Will they appear on TPB? By the way - Inagaki is one of my favourites - I am very grateful for Miyamoto Musashi trilogy. Thank You Polifem2009!
